title: Camp WeWow Space Week Day 2
description:
It's Space Week at Camp WeWow! Today, we're keeping our eyes up as we recreate the craters on our moon!! Visit tinkercast.com/resource/activity-make-some-moon-craters for directions to today's activity and share what you're tinkering with at tinkercast.com/share! If you could go anywhere in the universe, where would you go?! Call us at 1-888-7WOW-WOW to share! You just might get featured around the Camp WeWow Campfire this Friday!
